Introduction

Zuu is a singer under Vine Entertainment. She is a member of the girl group SECRET NUMBER.

On October 16, 2021, Zuu was revealed as a new member of SECRET NUMBER. She made her official debut as a member on October 27 with the single album "Fire Saturday".
